      <title>佛罗里达州新兴城市借款修复被飓风摧毁的码头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/rich-florida-boomtown-borrows-to-fix-pier-wiped-out-by-hurricane</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州那不勒斯正在利用市政债券市场来重建遭飓风伊恩摧毁的著名码头，这已是该市因极端天气破坏而进行的至少第五次重建。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/rich-florida-boomtown-borrows-to-fix-pier-wiped-out-by-hurricane</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 17:15:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
